Portions of `v3/crates/rvllm-vision/src/` are Rust ports of Hugging Face
Transformers revision 10555512868d663ee1ff627e4f5c5c260114235b:

  src/transformers/models/gemma4/modular_gemma4.py
    -> chat.rs, embedder.rs, lib.rs, loader.rs, model.rs
  src/transformers/models/gemma4/configuration_gemma4.py
    -> config.rs
  src/transformers/models/gemma4/image_processing_gemma4.py
    -> preprocess.rs
  src/transformers/models/gemma3n/modeling_gemma3n.py
    -> embedder.rs, model.rs
  src/transformers/masking_utils.py
    -> model.rs

The ports replace PyTorch modules with Rust/Candle inference code, remove
training and wrapper APIs, adapt weight-key lookup, inline the required masking
logic, and implement flat patch/position outputs. Later rvLLM changes add
checked loading, preprocessing parity fixes, and serving integration.

